LongRunningBroadcastService - Class in com.starsoft.serviseutil.main
Abstract class to create an intent service with CPU WakeLock control this service always runs as NOT STICKY and holding the lock CPU while doing the tasks (intents).
LongRunningBroadcastService(String) - Constructor for class com.starsoft.serviseutil.main.LongRunningBroadcastService
Creates an IntentService with WakeLock control Invoked by your subclass's constructor.
LongRunningReceiver - Class in com.starsoft.serviseutil.main
Abstract class for creating long-running broadcast receivers (by delegating the task to the intent service) Inherit from the abstract class LongRunningReceiver and implement the method getServiceClass() (You must return an object of class representative your service who will perform the task)
